DaynaPORT SCSI/Link Linux driver -- change history

0.2  2026-06-16
     - RX: poll continuously while frames are arriving -- re-issue the next
       READ(6) immediately when the previous one returned data, falling back to
       the cadence timer only on an empty poll.
     - New debug module parameter (off by default): logs per-READ RX yield and
       rate every 256 READs.

0.1  2026-06-15
     Initial release.
     - Builds as a loadable module against any configured Linux 2.4.x kernel.
